@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Persist data in SQLite

|Sales User|
start
:Submit form (e.g., Add Customer);

|CRM System|
:Receive POST request;
:Validate input;

if (Input valid?) then (Yes)
  :Open DB session/connection;
  :Insert/Update record in SQLite;
  :Commit transaction;
  :Flash success message;
  :Redirect to list page;
  stop
else (No)
  :Flash error message;
  :Redirect back to form;
  stop
endif

@enduml